      "bookSlug": "first-corinthians",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 8:3",
      "text": "ܐܢ ܐܢܫ ܕܝܢ ܡܚܒ ܠܐܠܗܐ ܗܢܐ ܐܬܝܕܥ ܡܢܗ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
