      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Corinthians 8:9",
      "text": "ܚܙܘ ܕܝܢ ܕܠܡܐ ܫܘܠܛܢܟܘܢ ܗܢܐ ܢܗܘܐ ܬܘܩܠܬܐ ܠܟܪܝܗܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "peshitta:first-corinthians.8.10",
